HEADWORD: Skunkhead
<hw>Skunk"head`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>The surf duck.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A duck
(<spn>Camptolaimus Labradorus</spn>) which formerly inhabited the
Atlantic coast of New England. It is now supposed to be extinct. Called
also <altname>Labrador duck</altname>, and <altname>pied
duck</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
